history.proof: intros m x y H1 H2 H3. split. - intros H4 z. unfold eqs, expo, exd, Iter_orb. split. + srun best use: impls_orb unfold: Iter_orb, impls. + strivial use: eqs_orb unfold: Iter_orb, eqs. - hfcrush use: expo_refl, expo_eq_exds_orb, expo_symm unfold: eqs.

ctx: intros m x y H1 H2 H3.
exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet +: Current bullet + is not finished.

ctx: intros m x y H1 H2 H3.
exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet -: Current bullet + is not finished.

original: intros m x y H1 H2 H3. split. - intros H4 z. unfold eqs, expo, exd, Iter_orb. split. + intros [H5 [i H6]]. split. * apply exds_orb_exd; auto. * exists i. rewrite <- H6. reflexivity. + intros [H5 [i H6]]. split. * apply exds_orb_exd; auto. * exists i. rewrite H6. reflexivity. - intros [H4 [i H5]]. split. + split. * apply exds_orb_exd; auto. * exists i. symmetry. apply H5. + split. * apply exds_orb_exd; auto. * exists i. apply H5.
